These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: tea, almond-milk, 7up, fanta
Sport: cricket, basketball, tennis, rowing
1. Beverage:tea is on the right of Sport:tennis##1
2. Sport:rowing is on the far left##1
3. Sport:tennis is between Sport:basketball and Beverage:almond-milk##2
4. Beverage:fanta is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:7up is between Beverage:almond-milk and Beverage:tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | fanta         | almond-milk   | 7up | tea       |
| Sport      | rowing | cricket | tennis   | basketball |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: board-games, sudoku, filmmaking, collecting
Nationality: malaysian, pakistani, australian, russian
1. Nationality:russian is between Hobby:filmmaking and Nationality:pakistani##2
2. Hobby:collecting is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:australian is on the right of Nationality:malaysian##1
4. Hobby:board-games is on the left of Nationality:malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku | board-games | filmmaking | collecting |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | russian   | malaysian | australian       |

